title: Pia Wurtzbach, Marlon Stockinger spend holiday in Hawaii
text:
Pia Wurtzbach, Marlon Stockinger spend holiday in Hawaii By Rosette Adel (philstar.com) | Updated December 31, 2016 - 6:36pm Rumored celebrity couple Miss Universe 2015 Pia Wurtzbach and car racer Marlon Stockinger were seen spending the holiday in Hawaii. Screenshot from Instagram/Pia Wurtzbach 
MANILA, Philippines â€“ Rumored celebrity couple Miss Universe 2015 Pia Wurtzbach and car racer Marlon Stockinger were seen spending the holiday in Hawaii. 
The two separately shared photos of them on their Instagram stories, with locations tagged in Waikiki beach, Honolulu, Hawaii. 
Pia even played paparazzi in her video where Marlon was candidly captured.
